title: NHTSA Product Information Catalog and Vehicle Listing - Home
description: The NHTSA Product Information Catalog and Vehicle Listing (vPIC) is a consolidated platform that presents data collected within the manufacturer reported data from 49 CFR Parts 551 – 595 for use in a variety of modern tools.
